{
  "texts": [
    "ti: Predicted bounding box coordinates (4 values: x, y, width, height) for anchor box i.",
    "p*i: Ground truth label for anchor box i (1 for foreground, 0 for background).",
    "L reg (t i, t * i): Regression loss for the predicted bounding box of anchor box i, often Smooth L1 loss.",
    "Mask R-CNN is a robust deep learning framework for object detection and instance segmentation.",
    "During object detection, it identifies and localizes objects within an image while incorporating instance-level context, which enables precise recognition of what the objects are and their locations."
  ]
}